data.description: Looking for that perfectly located subdivision with no HOA?  You found it.  This home offers 4 bedrooms and a loft with a cute little nook.  The 3rd floor can be your 4th bedroom or used as a bonus room for cozy movie nights.  If you need privacy, it will be perfect to use as an office away from everyone. Solar Panels in place to help save on utility bills.  Fenced, flat yard ready for cool nights by the fire pit. Close to shopping and restaurants and easy access to Downtown Fuquay, Raleigh and Holly Springs.
